TTB Label Verifier — Prototype Notice

This is a prototype system built for the U.S. Department of the Treasury,
Alcohol and Tobacco Tax and Trade Bureau (TTB), as a take-home assessment.

It is a demonstration prototype only. It is NOT:
  - an official TTB or U.S. Government system;
  - affiliated with, endorsed by, or representative of the TTB or the
    U.S. Department of the Treasury;
  - intended, authorized, or approved for production or operational use.

